	<div class="social-comment-body">
				<p>What I do like the first task for them is to put in a video (1 minute and a half) what they expect to learn in the course and why. They upload the video in a private channel between the first and the second class. Then I check them and I work to develop that skills in the course. After that, I made a control if they feel they get what they want and also a project they develop in all the course to see if they can do what they need.<br />
